arcz, Dating lacustrine episodes in the eastern Sahara by the epimerization of isoleucine in ostrich eggshells (1991) Palaeogeogr., Palaeoclimatol., Palaeoecol., 84, pp. 175-189; Petit-Marie, Interglacial environments in presently hyperarid Sahara: Paleoclimatic implications (1989) Palaeoclimatology and Palaeometeorology: Modern and Past Patterns of GlobalAtmospheric Transport, pp. 637-661. , M. Leinen, M. Sarnthein, Kluwer, Dordrecht; Petit-Marie, Will greenhouse green the Sahara? (1990) Episodes, 13, pp. 103-107; Rozanski, Araguás-Araguás, Gonfiantini, Isotopic patterns in modern global precipitation (1993) Continental Isotopic Indicators of Climate (Geophys. Monogr.), pp. 1-36. , P.K. Swart, K.C. Lohmann, J. McKenzie, S. Savin, Am. Geophys. Union, Washington, DC; Shackleton, Oxygen isotope analyses and paleotemperatures reassessed (1967) Nature, 215, pp. 15-17; Schild, Wendorf, Middle Paleolithic lakes in the Southwestern Desert of Egypt (1993) Egypt During the Last Interglacial: The Middle Paleolithic of Bir Tarfawi and Bir Sahara East, pp. 15-65. , F. Wendorf, R. Schild, A.E. Close, Plenum Press, New York; Schneider, Spätquartäre Produktivitätsänderungen im östlichen Angola-Becken: Reaktion auf Variationen im Passat-Monsun-Windsystem und in der Advektion des Benguela-Küstenstroms (1991) Thesis, p. 198. , Univ. Bremen; Schwarcz, Morawska, Uranium-series dating of carbonates from Bir Tarfawi and Bir Sahara East (1993) Egypt During the Last Interglacial: The Middle Paleolithic of Bir Tarfawi and Bir Sahara East, pp. 205-217. , F. Wendorf, R. Schild, A.E. Close, Plenum Press, New York; Siegenthaler, Oeschger, Correlation of O-18 in precipitation with temperature and altitude (1980) Nature, 285, pp. 314-317; Siegenthaler, Stable hydrogen and oxygen isotopes in the water cycle (1979) Lectures in Isotope Geology, pp. 264-273. , E. Jäger, J.C. Hunziker, Springer, Berlin; Sonntag, Thorweihe, Rudolph, Löhnert, Junghans, Münnich, Klitzsch, Swailem, Isotopic identification